1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,700
=Episode 21=
=A Man Slain By Two Lies=

11
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:53,350
If you don't choose me,

12
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:54,230
then go to hell!

13
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,670
I knew it.

14
00:01:01,350 --> 00:01:02,430
The moment I get married,

15
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:04,350
I get stabbed.

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,040
This farce

17
00:01:20,870 --> 00:01:22,000
ends now.

18
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:27,430
Li Hong.

19
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:29,270
Confess it.

20
00:01:30,310 --> 00:01:31,150
You can't get away.

21
00:01:34,790 --> 00:01:36,640
You think a livestream can ruin me?

22
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,760
People forget fast.

23
00:01:39,350 --> 00:01:40,870
As long as I send you all to hell,

24
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,310
the Li family will be mine.

25
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,960
Ye Lang.

26
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,790
Leave now. Don't worry about me.

27
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:47,560
I'm not leaving you behind.

28
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:51,960
Hong, no!

29
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,310
Ye Lang!

30
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,120
Don't be scared.

31
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:20,750
I'm here.

32
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:26,840
What a tragic pair of lovers.

33
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:30,030
One took a bullet for love,
the other willingly acted as bait.

34
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,030
Quite a show.

35
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,120
Xue.

36
00:02:34,820 --> 00:02:35,870
These two lives

37
00:02:36,190 --> 00:02:37,430
are my gift to you.

38
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,910
Which one you want first?

39
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,640
Xue, what are you doing?

40
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,870
The truth is, your heart

41
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,240
had no problem,

42
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,560
the one I replaced was the bad one.

43
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,120
If you really love me,

44
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,360
then the one who should die now

45
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:07,080
is you.

46
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:12,870
Hong.

47
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,680
Hong!

48
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:17,000
Do you love me?

49
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,360
Hong.

50
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,200
Hong.

51
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,120
Hong!

52
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,870
I love you.

53
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,200
Hong.

54
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,120
Hong.

55
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:37,910
What's wrong, Hong?

56
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,470
What's wrong, Hong?

57
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,470
Are you okay?

58
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,640
Hong!

59
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,840
Hong!

60
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,310
He's already dead.

61
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,520
He had it coming.

62
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,840
Xiaodi...

63
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,430
Xiaodi saved us.

64
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:58,960
Don't worry.

65
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:03,680
It's all over now.

66
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,000
Thanks to this hidden camera.

67
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,840
Otherwise,

68
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,000
I wouldn't have found where you were.

69
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,520
So,

70
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:21,430
you came to save me

71
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,360
or Murong Xue?

72
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,430
Being jealous?

73
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,720
Looks like you're doing fine.

74
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,200
What are you doing?

75
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,360
What comes next

76
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,120
isn't good for it to witness.

77
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,600
So in our previous life,

78
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,600
Li Hong used Xiaodi's death

79
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,240
to make me misunderstand you

80
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,720
and had me kill you?

81
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:05,040
You're seriously going to

82
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,720
bring up another man's name in my bed?

83
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,440
Have some shame.

84
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,040
In the previous life,

85
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:16,510
you pressed a dagger against my back.

86
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:18,870
But you hesitated.

87
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,040
While you were hesitating,

88
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,360
you wanted answers from me.

89
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,750
Then that man showed up,

90
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,480
he took your hand

91
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:28,790
and drove it in.

92
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,160
Tell me

93
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:36,310
about our previous life.

94
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,600
That ghost marriage

95
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:43,560
was where we began.

96
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,830
I fell for you at first sight

97
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:49,070
and hid who I was.

98
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:51,350
Later,

99
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:52,920
I took you to a fishing village,

100
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,430
living like an ordinary couple.

101
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:58,800
You taught me how to pick fish.

102
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:01,140
I roasted you sweet potatoes.

103
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,270
Back then,

104
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:08,000
I almost forgot who I was.

105
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:11,140
I only remembered
I loved you a lot.

106
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:17,720
We decorated

107
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,070
this villa together.

108
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,150
That blanket

109
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,360
was the one you picked at first sight.

110
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,070
And that colorful ceramic plate,

111
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,430
we made it together.

112
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,390
So none of it was coincidence.

113
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,920
No wonder it felt so familiar.

114
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,350
It turns out

115
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,830
we really did live here before.

116
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,230
Niannian.

117
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,110
I'm sorry.

118
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,160
In the previous life,

119
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,870
you weren't very happy.

120
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,750
After the Li family took us back,

121
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,560
I said I'd help cure Xiaodi,

122
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,040
but in the end, I still lost him.

123
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,390
In this life,

124
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,360
I only kept him a few days longer.

125
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,320
It's not your fault.

126
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,560
Don't worry.

127
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,400
In this life,

128
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,920
we'll be happy till the very end.

129
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,000
Xiaodi,

130
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,310
since you left,

131
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,600
the world feels so empty.

132
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,230
Xiaodi,

133
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,080
I swear

134
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,160
I'll protect Jiang Niannian with my life.

135
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,600
She will never suffer again.

136
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:34,870
I'll come see you often.

137
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,390
Ye Lang,

138
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:47,910
I think something's off.

139
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,200
Xiaodi was bedridden for years.

140
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,510
His overall condition wasn't great.

141
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:55,840
His heart function was weak too.

142
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,320
By all logic,

143
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,870
he shouldn't have been a donor.

144
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:03,240
If fate can't be changed,

145
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:07,000
then what happened before must happen again.

146
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,120
I'll definitely meet

147
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,600
the people I met.

148
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,790
If Li Hong was used too,

149
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,720
then that person can only be...

150
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,150
Murong Xue.

151
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:25,390
In the previous life, you barely knew her.

152
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:26,870
I suspect

153
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,360
she's like me,

154
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,510
reborn with memories of the past.

155
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:41,780
Hello?

156
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,680
Young Master,

157
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,020
Master had a sudden heart attack,

158
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,960
being treated now.

159
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,600
Looks not good.

160
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:51,510
Contact Manlong's top cardiologists.

161
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,320
I'm on my way.

162
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,920
- Niannian...
- Just go.

163
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,390
Your father needs you.

164
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,590
What about you?

165
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,840
I don't think

166
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,320
he wants to see me.

167
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,860
Besides,

168
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:06,960
what you just said,

169
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,200
I need to verify it.

170
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,750
Now,

171
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:24,790
the company can only be entrusted to you.

172
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:27,150
I've already arranged

173
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,670
the share transfer.

174
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,720
Since I was little,

175
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:34,630
you only cared for family and interests.

176
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,150
And now you're forcing me into this position?

177
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,120
What happened with Li Hong

178
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,630
has too much impact.

179
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,910
Other corporations

180
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,030
are all waiting for us

181
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,030
to collapse.

182
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,670
At a time like this,

183
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,390
someone has to

184
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,120
hold everything together.

185
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:57,390
Tell me

186
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,550
other than you,

187
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,360
do I have any other choice?

188
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:09,710
I'm sorry.

189
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,000
This is all my fault.

190
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,670
If I had stopped Li Hong,

191
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,480
your brother wouldn't have...

192
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,840
Li Hong is behind all of this.

193
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,360
It's all because of him

194
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:28,030
Li Group is drowning in scandal.

195
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,710
I'm thinking

196
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:30,960
of holding an exhibition

197
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:33,020
of Ye Mei's works
at Manlong Art Museum.

198
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,840
It could help restore
the Li Group's reputation,

199
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:38,030
kinda a gift to Ye Lang.

200
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,870
You and him

201
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,320
grew up together.

202
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,840
You've seen Ye Mei paint.

203
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,750
If you curate it,

204
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,240
it might help resolve

205
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,630
the current public backlash.

206
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,870
You two are really in love.

207
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,680
Niannian.

208
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,270
Actually,

209
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,390
I brought you a gift.

210
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,790
Auntie Ye gave this to me.

211
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:11,550
It's never been shown publicly.

212
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,180
Take it as my donation
to the exhibition.

213
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,800
This is...

214
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,480
This is my mother.

215
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,550
She passed away very early.

216
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:25,630
To comfort me,
Auntie Ye painted this portrait for me

217
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,960
based on my description.

218
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:32,120
That year,

219
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:34,550
your mother and I

220
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:36,240
left the family

221
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:40,790
and lived in a southern town for three years.

222
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,630
After you were born,

223
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,030
I thought life

224
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,360
would stay this happy forever.

225
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,910
Until the board of directors

226
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:56,150
used your grandparents' lives

227
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,270
to force me back

228
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,960
and take this position.

229
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:05,750
Ye Lang,

230
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,440
do you know

231
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:11,630
heirs of families like ours

232
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,630
don't get to have true love.

233
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:18,360
We can only submit

234
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,150
to the family's interests.

235
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,320
Now I see.

236
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:38,920
Ye Lang,

237
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:54,320
marry Jiang Niannian.

238
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,080
Back then,

239
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,390
I failed to protect your mother

240
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,030
and give you

241
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,080
a whole family.

242
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:08,870
But you are

243
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:10,840
braver than I was,

244
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,080
and luckier than me.

245
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:14,710
I believe

246
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:16,750
you and her

247
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,910
won't end up

248
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:21,510
repeating your mother and me.

249
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,320
I'm old.

250
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,390
I can't do much more for you.

251
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:32,480
Some roads,

252
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:35,790
you have to walk on your own

253
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,390
to really understand them.

254
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,920
Father,

255
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:45,710
I promise you

256
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,750
I'll protect the Li family

257
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,960
and keep Jiang Niannian safe.

258
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:16,810
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

259
00:15:18,650 --> 00:15:24,850
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

260
00:15:25,410 --> 00:15:32,410
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

261
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:35,610
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

262
00:15:35,610 --> 00:15:40,610
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

263
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:44,850
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

264
00:15:45,370 --> 00:15:49,290
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

265
00:15:49,330 --> 00:15:53,130
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

266
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:58,890
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

267
00:15:58,890 --> 00:16:03,210
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

268
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:07,050
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

269
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:11,570
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

270
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:16,410
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

271
00:16:16,810 --> 00:16:23,370
♪Life finds its way again♪
